%N A081308 Number of ways to write n as sum of a prime and an 3-smooth number.
%C A081308 Asymptotically, for n coprime to 6, a(n) ~ C*n on the average, with C=3/(2*log(2)*log(3))~1.969796..., see the link. - _M. F. Hasler_, Oct 21 2011
